Pad texts with a character filler

# Arguments

- a_type  : Types of alignment ["Left", "right", "center"] ( trimmed )
- a_width : Total width of padded chunk [ Unsigned integer ] 
- a_fill  : A character to fill
- a_text  : Text to pad


# Demo

```
<-$pad(center,18,^,HEADER)->
===
<-^^^^^^HEADER^^^^^^->
```

# Test

$assert(Hello***,$pad(left  ,8,*,Hello))
$assert(***Hello,$pad(right ,8,*,Hello))
$assert(**Hello*,$pad(center,8,*,Hello))
